er exploded and the carts freely shot down the hill. Evander looked at the Macedonians scamper off and then rode after the three carts. He rode past one and unleashed his sword holding it beside him as he cut  a nearby tree. The small tree fell before one cart and got tangled in the carts wheel stopping it. He continued and rode up beside the second cart slashing the wooden tires stopping it in it's tracks. He followed close behind the last one as it reached the shore line with the most deadly cliffs in all over Thessaly. He flipped off his Horse and landed on the cart hanging off the back. He struggled to climb up as he heard the villagers screaming. Evander reached the top of the cart and cut off the back of the cart. One by one the villagers jumped off and rolled on the grass until the last one, a little brown haired girl. Evander swung down and in grabbed her just as the cart hit the edge and jumped out the back just as the cart tipped over the cliff hurling towards the sea rocks. Evander rolled protecting the girl and regained his balance on the grass. The villagers collected each other and walked back to the village. The Macedonians got away, Evander wasn't satisfied. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm24.showMessage?topicID=8.topic"> << Prev Topic </a> &nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm24.showMessage?topicID=4.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm24.emailToFriend?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend">